    "Name": "Remix PRW-RMX",
    "Details": "The Remix PRW-RMX is a one-of-a-kind 65-ton Project Rewrite design combining salvaged Word of Blake technology with Clan Diamond Shark hardware. A right-arm Retractable Blade provides melee capability alongside a left-arm Bloodhound Active Probe and two Clan ER Medium Lasers. The right torso mounts an MML 9 with separate LRM and SRM bins, while a left-torso LB-5X carries both standard and cluster ammunition. Dual CASE II installations and a head-mounted Laser AMS complete the defensive package.\n\n<b><color=#e62e00>Quirk: Rugged</color></b>\n\n<b><color=#e62e00>Drop Cost Multiplier: 1.09</color></b>",
    "Icon": "NEEDS_ICON"
  },
